title: Learn Spanish Vocabulary 4 Books in 1 by Flashcard eBooks(.epub)
description:
Learn Spanish Vocabulary - English/Spanish Flashcards - 4 Books in 1 by Flashcard eBooks 

Requirements: .ePUB Reader

Overview: Help your child improve their Spanish vocabulary knowledge quickly and easily, with more than 250 beautifully illustrated Flashcards .

Learn Spanish Vocabulary - English/Spanish Flashcards:
Animals
Clothes
101 Household Items
Numbers, Shapes and Colors

Each book contains pronunciation aids (that are easy to read) aswell as the English alternative for each word. 
These unique Flashcards are the perfect way for adults and children to read, speak and remember over 250 Spanish words.
This edition contains four books from the popular 'Flashcard Ebooks - Spanish' series, 
This book is sure to become a treasured companion on your journey to learn and improve your Spanish vocabulary.

Genre: Non-Fiction > Educational
